original: Blogsnobs lets you share your life, chronicle your darkest secrets, express your dreams, plot to kill your wife, connect with the lonely, the lascivious and the lethargic. It is your journal - here for the world to read.
translated: 你可以在Blogsnobs分享你的生活点滴，记录你内心深处的秘密，说出你昨晚的怪梦，谋划杀妻，还能与孤独者、淫荡者和嗜睡者共同交流。这是你的个人日志——全世界人都能读到。

original: The world revolves around blogs. Blogs are more important than journalism. Because they're about you and your feelings. We fill the Intertubes with pointless musings about life, politics and love from attention-seeking narcissists with far too much time on their hands.
translated: 地球绕着博客转。它比新闻都重要，毕竟博客关注的是你和你的感受。它为那些吃饱了撑着的自恋狂创造了渠道，向网络倾倒人生与爱情的无病呻吟和键盘政治，博人眼球。

original: Just like how people get married when their relationship starts to get boring, so too do people start blogs when they run out of things to say. Tell the world about your scintillating daily routine. Communicate your perceptive views on life. Take a picture of the asschowder you made after last night's all-you-can-eat Indian buffet. Kid yourselves that millions of total strangers are going to be interested in what you had for lunch. The blogosphere matters.
translated: 一如婚姻是爱情的坟墓，写博客的人没活了也是如此。向世界展示你闪闪发光的日常生活吧。用你独到的见解锐评。拍下昨晚煮的炸厨房大餐。骗自己会有几百万人对你今天吃什么感兴趣。不能没有博客圈。

original: I really have amazing taste in music...

Can you believe it?!! I got sacked from work last week. SEXIST PIGS!!! My boss said that he was sorry to see me go but he could not condone naked vogueing at an office function, especially with children present...
translated: 你敢相信吗？！！上周我被公司开除了。这帮性别歧视的猪头！！！老板说他也不想我走人，但他实在忍受不了我在办公室活动上裸体走秀，更何况当时还有小孩在场...

original: I'm spring cleaning today in my booty shorts, just because I can. My neighbor came round earlier to borrow some milk and was checking me out so badly...
translated: 今天我没事做，就穿着热裤来了个春季大扫除。几天前邻居问我借了些牛奶，借的时候还不忘细细打量我一番...

original: OH MY GOD!!! Lisa is going to be here - in San Fierro - for some LARPing festival and she wants to me meet me!! I am so excited and nervous. I can't wait to pretend we're being invaded by goblins...
translated: 我的天哪！！！Lisa要来了！来到圣辉洛！是来参加什么扮演节的，还想顺路见我一面！！我既兴奋，又紧张。我等不及想假装我们被地精入侵了...

original: Nobody reads your blog Melissa. And I'll tell you why. First off, you can't spell worth a shit. It's not teh. It's "the." And you mispronounce everything in real life too. It's not Jeeeeeeuuuum. It's gym...
translated: 真没人看你的博客，Melissa。我告诉你为什么。首先，你连字都打不明白。不是「teh」，是「the」。而且你平常就是话都说不清楚。不是「Jeeeeeeuuuum」，是「gym」...

original: Sorry for not updating for so long but I've been dying of a broken heart. I'm hurt. I'm lost. I'm crying. I'm wet. Even pottery club cannot lift my spirits...
translated: 很抱歉，一直没有更新，但我就要心碎而死了。我受伤了，我迷失了，我哭了，我湿了。就连陶艺社都不能让我打起精神...

original: Nobody enters the house. EVER. Except for Boo Boo Wilkins, of course. Here kitty kitty. He killed a bird today and I ejaculated...
translated: 没人进过我家。从来没有。当然，除了Boo Boo Wilkins。过来，猫咪猫咪。今天他杀了一只小鸟，我射精了...

original: I'm new to this blogging thing.
